org.spongepowered.api.data.value.mutable

Interface SetValue<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of elements supported
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseValue<Set<E>>, CollectionValue<E,Set<E>,SetValue<E>,ImmutableSetValue<E>>, Iterable<E>, Value<Set<E>>

    public interface SetValue<E>
extends CollectionValue<E,Set<E>,SetValue<E>,ImmutableSetValue<E>>
    Represents a type of CollectionValue backed by a Set. The reasoning is that a Set retains no ordering of the elements it contains.
